OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776246948
OL,3,CBlind artist achieves 'world first'
OL,4,Crunning marathon guided by AI glasses
OL,6,FA blind artist has achieved a world
OL,7,Ffirst by running a marathon guided by
OL,8,Fartificial intelligence glasses,
OL,9,Fassisted by remote volunteers.
OL,11,FClarke Reynolds, known as Braille
OL,12,Fcreative Mr Dot, completed the
OL,13,FBrighton Marathon on Sunday aided by
OL,14,Fsmart glasses.
OL,16,FThey were connected to an app which
OL,17,Fenlists volunteers across the world to
OL,18,Fsupport visually impaired people in
OL,19,Fdaily tasks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
