PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776246948
OL,3,CBlind artist achieves 'world first'
OL,4,Crunning marathon guided by AI glasses
OL,6,FIt is usually used by people choosing
OL,7,Fwhat to wear, or locating items in a
OL,8,Ffridge, so Clarke pushed it beyond its
OL,9,Fusual usage.
OL,11,FHe is believed to be the first to use
OL,12,Fit to run the 26.2-mile course in aid
OL,13,Fof the Fight for Sight charity, of
OL,14,Fwhich he is an ambassador for.
OL,16,FThe 45-year-old from Portsmouth said
OL,17,Fhis goal had been achieved with the
OL,18,Fhelp of "hundreds of people from all
OL,19,Fover the world ` from Croydon to
OL,20,FKansas and Belfast to Bahrain".
OL,26,@zD@IOU|D@^O]
