PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776246948
OL,3,CBlind artist achieves 'world first'
OL,4,Crunning marathon guided by AI glasses
OL,6,F"I've raised awareness and sparked so
OL,7,Fmany conversations which I hope will
OL,8,Fhelp to challenge society's ideas
OL,9,Fabout what blind people can do", he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FPre-selected volunteers were able to
OL,13,Fsee exactly what was in front of Mr
OL,14,FReynolds and cheer him on as he
OL,15,Fcompleted the race on Sunday in just
OL,16,Funder six hours and 20 minutes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
