PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776246948
OL,3,CBlind artist achieves 'world first'
OL,4,Crunning marathon guided by AI glasses
OL,6,FDescribing his experience using the
OL,7,Fapp to train for the marathon, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "I have 10 seconds to say 'Hi
OL,9,FI'm Clarke, I'm training to run a
OL,10,Fmarathon'. They see me. They're
OL,11,Fexpecting me to ask 'where is the
OL,12,Fsoup?' Or help me to a shop.
OL,14,F"So, they are pretty blown away when I
OL,15,Fsay I'm training for the Brighton
OL,16,FMarathon. Some have even offered to
OL,17,Fsponsor me.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776246948
OL,3,CBlind artist achieves 'world first'
OL,4,Crunning marathon guided by AI glasses
OL,6,F"I love the idea that hundreds of
OL,7,Fpeople from all over the world ` from
OL,8,FCroydon to Kansas and Belfast to
OL,9,FBahrain ` will have helped me to
OL,10,Fachieve it.
OL,12,FMr Reynolds has so far raised #2,700
OL,13,Ffor national charity Fight for Sight,
OL,14,Fwhich funds research into eye
OL,15,Fconditions as well as funding
OL,16,Fnationwide support projects. Among
OL,17,Fthose sponsoring Mr Reynolds was TV
OL,18,Fpresenter Victoria Coren Mitchell.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776246948
OL,3,CBlind artist achieves 'world first'
OL,4,Crunning marathon guided by AI glasses
OL,6,F"I love making the connection with
OL,7,Fpeople, telling them about why I'm
OL,8,Frunning, and about Fight for Sight's
OL,9,Fwork. They are always really
OL,10,Finterested and love being part of
OL,11,Fsomething so out of the ordinary. We
OL,12,Fchat as I run," he said.
OL,14,FMr Reynolds has the inherited eye
OL,15,Fcondition retinitis pigmentosa and
OL,16,Fdescribes his 5% vision as "like
OL,17,Flooking underwater".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@OO]xD@\OUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
