FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776246948
OL,3,CBlind artist achieves 'world first'
OL,4,Crunning marathon guided by AI glasses
OL,6,FHe had previously completed the London
OL,7,FMarathon with a guide, and was joined
OL,8,Fby trained guide runner Alastair
OL,9,FRatcliffe as a backup safety
OL,10,Fprecaution.
OL,12,FFight for Sight's director of impact
OL,13,Fand external affairs, Eleanor
OL,14,FSouthwood, said: "We are so proud of
OL,15,FClarke. What he has achieved is
OL,16,Fextraordinary.
OL,18,F"We are so grateful to him for his
OL,19,Fsupport and to everyone who has so
OL,20,Fgenerously sponsored him."
OL,26,@vD@ROUzD@AOU|D@ZO]
